{"tid":1788115,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色經濟圈航空公司篇","createTime":"2019-12-18T11:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T06:36:59.000Z","uid":127929,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"874d194e0091ddc15cfe8b33ff277faa0573e50e","tid":1788115,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T11:47:44.000Z","msg":"航空公司就難啲講邊間係黃，但至少可以知道邊間係狗也不屌既垃圾航空公司<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港航空</strong></span><br />\n支那紅底既資金黑洞黎，呢間野<span style=\"color: red;\">本身有欠債</span>，12月借返黎既支那資金好快又會洗哂<span style=\"color: red;\">冇錢還債</span>，然後唔夠錢比人釘牌，買左機票既真係食得屎(因為連中銀都改撚左個保險條款，<span style=\"color: red;\">保險肯定唔會有得賠錢</span>) btw, <span style=\"color: red;\">香港航空退機票冇得退錢仲要比額外手續費</span>(可能有啲有得退)，航班平均delay個零鐘係基本，準時飛係笑話黎，買左港航機票第日冇得飛等住硬食貴機票啦(搶到既話)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">港航垃圾狗也不屌</span>，所有人幾平都咪撚買，機組人員<span style=\"color: red;\">勿</span>辭職，可以揾定勞工處迫佢準時出糧，請組職公會罷佢老母工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>國泰/港龍</strong></span><br />\n管理層請自重，你地係染紅緊既垃圾黎，管理層再迫員工互督灰既話等罷工喇屌你老母，香港人請預設揀外國航空司先，冇先考慮CX<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>外國航空公司</strong></span><br />\n所有外國航空公司可考慮，支那公司除外，SG Australia呢啲奶共閪國家如非工作請少去"},{"pid":"cbca253f8c81c7ecdde1ef80ceb7b9a0a5213954","tid":1788115,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T11:50:10.000Z","msg":"大家壓力大去散心正常，但希望大家去少啲留返啲錢捐比星火"},{"pid":"9e41bda1282f951e0dee566ddc1b66874a861e01","tid":1788115,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T11:51:28.000Z","msg":"我地要港航繼續成為資金黑洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2bd5359866e5740ed1ffffda4dbaf5828c7e42","tid":1788115,"uid":225798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T11:52:24.000Z","msg":"Ban 9 SQ 啦"},{"pid":"3ad935b94673cfaa4bb21f15068d5387804ac5fc","tid":1788115,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T11:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e6f7594adf95551425aba585e8b469e14a32f5","tid":1788115,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:01:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">最好當然係唔去旅行留返啲錢捐比星火</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1423f0adfbb57f8c5454f781444575103cf713c","tid":1788115,"uid":161440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0e6f7594adf95551425aba585e8b469e14a32f5","tid":1788115,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:01:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">最好當然係唔去旅行留返啲錢捐比星火</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425b53585f52ee7bb588be73a72c5c51019a4935","tid":1788115,"uid":44598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:10:58.000Z","msg":"其實hk express黃定藍"},{"pid":"f55eaeb0ccc2c92b2d4c7032c2a51dcc8a84483d","tid":1788115,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"425b53585f52ee7bb588be73a72c5c51019a4935","tid":1788115,"uid":44598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:10:58.000Z","msg":"其實hk express黃定藍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:12:09.000Z","msg":"hk express 比國泰買左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b3ef6abe0eb87b0575225e0a41c67b10cc9bc5","tid":1788115,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:13:40.000Z","msg":"阿聯猶呢？"},{"pid":"16ed6f4829481bbbfe1467cfd782c4e35a80c13d","tid":1788115,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:20:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">剛避過釘牌危機 香港航空遭機管局扣起7架飛機</span></span><br />\n12月16日(一) 23:24更新 18:22建立<br />\n<br />\n財困纏身的香港航空剛逃過被空運牌照局「釘牌」厄運後，又再爆出欠款醜聞。消息指，<span style=\"color: red;\">港航因欠款，遭機管局扣押7架飛機，每架飛機涉及欠款數以千萬元計，若港航不還款將拍賣飛機以抵欠債。</span>機管局證實，根據機管局條例第40條，扣留香港航空7架閒置的飛機，以保障財務權益。據機管局了解被扣留的飛機最近幾個月已沒有用作載客用途。<br />\n<br />\n港航去年起傳出財困消息，今年財政狀況進一步惡化，千餘員工上月薪酬亦延期發放。空運牌照局本月初(2日)向港航頒令兩項新附加條件，觸發「釘牌」危機，不少已買港航機票的旅客均憂心忡忡。<span style=\"color: red;\">港航的母公司海南航空控股當晚在上海證券交易所公布，已申請40億元人民幣貸款(約44億港元)，終暫獲放生，但當局明言會繼續密切監察其財困狀況，「計時炸彈」仍有機會引爆。</span><br />\n<br />\nsource: 白粉報"},{"pid":"b2f8c78ca721a9db31554d398dbe1f829605c188","tid":1788115,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14b3ef6abe0eb87b0575225e0a41c67b10cc9bc5","tid":1788115,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:13:40.000Z","msg":"阿聯猶呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:22:07.000Z","msg":"如非工作需要，建議留返啲錢捐比星火<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43de21d17fd6ff9b4886c350f0824e990a79ea94","tid":1788115,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T13:43:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2c44bb7d7048e382b0892b143b7177bc09d3ac","tid":1788115,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65c6d5cb3db572c335c0ea2510dc401db04c98a","tid":1788115,"uid":31841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:45:50.000Z","msg":"因為為航權問題，無一間航空公司會係黃，完"},{"pid":"83e0f42637def7bcb44be5a087c328d990c7ffc6","tid":1788115,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:49:48.000Z","msg":"阿聯酋迫啲香港空姐掛中國國旗"},{"pid":"4c4d736c04654cd5ed6b307c08d61a6b4a42e3c3","tid":1788115,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:32:18.000Z","msg":"其實好多都跪低晒變左支那香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e186524e66f46d9b5bee8a4c4234a200f860e3ec","tid":1788115,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:33:36.000Z","msg":"中華航空<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9969ed9d5d948894853eeb3d70addcc40f7365a0","tid":1788115,"uid":259777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:36:59.000Z","msg":"之前逼航空公司改台灣做中國台灣只有美國三大航空同台灣長榮中華冇跪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"e0e6f7594adf95551425aba585e8b469e14a32f5","tid":1788115,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:01:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">最好當然係唔去旅行留返啲錢捐比星火</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}